    {
        "content": "<p>It's not <em>exactly</em> what you ask for because it doesn't throw away the <code>⊥</code> terms, but that should likely be a distinct operation anyway</p>",
        "id": 489929937,
        "sender_full_name": "Yaël Dillies",
        "timestamp": 1734604036
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Annoyingly, <code>disjointed</code> hasn't yet been generalised away from sequences</p>",
